   as the quotient space 
  
    
      
        
          
            R
          
          
            2
          
        
        
          /
        
        
          
            Z
          
          
            2
          
        
      
    
    {\displaystyle \mathbb {R} ^{2}/\mathbb {Z} ^{2}}
  , Arnold's cat map is the transformation 
  
    
      
